reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Contains everything you could need in an emergency!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased this first aid kit, and I am VERY pleased with the quality and contents. The kit comes in a very sturdy, waterproof carrying case and has two main pockets that are easily accessible and the elastic bands that keep the supplies in place.The kit contains a wide variety of supplies, including a thermometer, cooling gel patches, bandaids, emergency blanket, tourniquets, gauze rolls, instant ice packs, gloves, tape, and cpr mask. All of the items are of good quality and exactly what you would need in an emergency.This kit is a great value and I would highly recommend it to anyone. I have used it several times already and am very pleased with the quality of the supplies and the fact that everything is so well organized and easy to find.I would give this product 5 stars all day long! To anyone who is looking for a quality first aid kit, this is definitely the one to get. You won't be disappointed.
